'''苏马迈体育场'''（{{Lang-ar|ملعب الثمامة|Malʿab ath-Thumāma}}）是一座位于[[卡塔尔|卡塔尔]][[多哈|多哈]]{{le|苏马迈|Al Thumama (Doha)}}的体育场，在2021年10月22日正式開放。这座体育场會舉行[[2022年國際足協世界盃|2022年國際足協世界盃]]賽事。

== 历史 ==
申办世界杯前，卡塔尔原计划在苏马迈体育场的位置修建一座地下足球场。按照原方案，这座球场的场地和观众席都在地平面以下，可容纳1.1万人。地下体育场工程在2008年开始了挖掘工作。不过，伴随卡塔尔申办世界杯一事取得进展，地下体育场建设暂停。<ref name="instead_of_underground">{{Cite news |url=http://stadiumdb.com/news/2015/12/qatar_2022_world_cup_instead_of_underground_stadium |title=Qatar 2022: World Cup instead of “underground stadium” |date=2015-12-28 |work=StadiumDB.com |accessdate=2020-11-28 |language=en |archive-date=2017-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908033813/http://stadiumdb.com/news/2015/12/qatar_2022_world_cup_instead_of_underground_stadium |dead-url=no }}</ref>卡塔尔竞争2022年世界杯足球赛主办权时，申办计划中并没有苏马迈体育场。<ref name="new_design_like_a_decorative">{{Cite news |url=http://stadiumdb.com/news/2017/08/new_design_like_a_decorative_headdress |title=New design: Like a decorative headdress |date=2017-08-20 |work=StadiumDB.com |accessdate=2020-11-28 |language=en |archive-date=2020-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200624024935/http://stadiumdb.com/news/2017/08/new_design_like_a_decorative_headdress |dead-url=no }}</ref>卡塔尔赢得主办权后，原计划的12座球场减为8座。2015年12月，卡塔尔宣布将把8座球场之一建在苏马迈。<ref name="qatar_2022_world_cup">{{Cite news |url=http://stadiumdb.com/news/2015/12/qatar_2022_world_cup_stadium_every_6_miles |title=Qatar 2022: World Cup stadium every 6 miles?! |date=2015-12-04 |work=StadiumDB.com |accessdate=2020-11-28 |language=en |archive-date=2020-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701041104/http://stadiumdb.com/news/2015/12/qatar_2022_world_cup_stadium_every_6_miles |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="instead_of_underground" />

苏马迈体育场的前期工作在2016年展开。2017年3月1日，体育场正式破土动工。<ref name="ornamental_facade">{{Cite news |url=http://stadiumdb.com/news/2020/01/qatar_2022_ornamental_facade_of_al_thumama_ready |title=Qatar 2022: Ornamental facade of Al Thumama ready |date=2020-01-30 |work=StadiumDB.com |accessdate=2020-11-28 |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209023543/http://stadiumdb.com/news/2020/01/qatar_2022_ornamental_facade_of_al_thumama_ready |dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年8月，体育场的设计方案正式亮相<ref name="gulf-times">{{Cite news |url=https://gulf-times.com/story/560840 |title=Thumama stadium: 'Gahfiya,' design reflects harmony between heritage, future |date=2017-08-20 |work=Gulf Times |accessdate=2020-11-28 |language=en |archive-date=2018-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180806023215/http://www.gulf-times.com/story/560840 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="new_design_like_a_decorative" />。2017年10月，混凝土浇筑工程开始。<ref name="thepeninsulaqatar">{{Cite news |url=http://wap.thepeninsulaqatar.com/article/09/10/2017/First-concrete-poured-at-Al-Thumama-Stadium |title=First concrete poured at Al Thumama Stadium |date=2017-10-09 |work=The Peninsula |accessdate=2020-11-28 |language=en}}</ref>2018年，苏马迈体育场获{{le|建筑评论未来项目奖|MIPIM AR Future Projects Award}}<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://chinese.aljazeera.net/news/2018/10/26/qatar-2022-world-cup-stadiums-all-you-need-know |title=卡塔尔2022年世界杯体育场馆：你需要知道的一切 |date=2018-10-26 |work=aljazeera |accessdate=2020-11-28 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118150553/https://chinese.aljazeera.net/news/2018/10/26/qatar-2022-world-cup-stadiums-all-you-need-know }}</ref>。2019年3月，混凝土工作完成<ref name="thepeninsulaqatar-Concrete ">{{Cite news |url=https://thepeninsulaqatar.com/article/10/03/2019/Concrete-works-completed-at-Qatar-2022-Stadium-in-Al-Thumama |title=Concrete works completed at Qatar 2022 Stadium in Al Thumama |date=2019-03-10 |work=The Peninsula |accessdate=2020-11-28 |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208100256/https://thepeninsulaqatar.com/article/10/03/2019/Concrete-works-completed-at-Qatar-2022-Stadium-in-Al-Thumama |dead-url=no }}</ref>。体育场原计划在2020年9月15日完工<ref name="ornamental_facade" />。完工时间后来推迟至2021年<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://en.as.com/en/2020/05/14/football/1589474963_134750.html |title=World Cup 2022: No delay to works on Al-Thumama and Lusail Stadiums |date=2020-05-14 |work=as |accessdate=2020-11-28 |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209070419/https://en.as.com/en/2020/05/14/football/1589474963_134750.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://en.as.com/en/2020/11/16/football/1605548691_030137.html |title=2022 Qatar: Al Thumama World Cup stadium will be completed in 2021 |date=2020-11-16 |work=as |accessdate=2020-11-28 |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231133635/https://en.as.com/en/2020/11/16/football/1605548691_030137.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

按照计划，苏马迈体育场将承办2022年世界杯足球赛小组赛至四分之一决赛阶段的比赛，世界杯期间的观众容量为4万人。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://chinese.aljazeera.net/sport-culture/2020/11/23/你需要了解的关于2022年世界杯体育场的一切 |title=你需要了解的关于2022年世界杯体育场的一切 |date=2020-11-23 |work=aljazeera |accessdate=2020-11-28 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123114144/https://chinese.aljazeera.net/sport-culture/2020/11/23/%E4%BD%A0%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E2022%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%9D%AF%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2%E5%9C%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87 |dead-url=no }}</ref>世界杯后，体育场将拆除上层看台，将容量减小至2万人。<ref name="Legacy" /><ref name="heerim" />

== 建筑 ==
苏马迈体育场由卡塔尔建筑师易卜拉辛·穆罕默德·宰达（Ibrahim M. Jaidah）同{{link-ko|熙林综合建筑师事务所|희림종합건축사사무소}}联合设计<ref name="new_design_like_a_decorative" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sc.qa/en/news/six-facts-about-al-thumama-stadium|title=Six facts about Al Thumama Stadium - the latest 2022 FIFA World Cup venue|date=2017-08-20|publisher=Qatar 2022 FIFA World Cup Supreme Committee|accessdate=2020-11-28|language=en|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622165931/https://www.sc.qa/en/news/six-facts-about-al-thumama-stadium|dead-url=no}}</ref>，总承包商为卡塔尔的贾贝尔工程公司和土耳其的泰克芬建筑安装公司。<ref name="heerim_to_design">{{Cite news |url=http://stadiumdb.com/news/2017/04/qatar_2022_heerim_to_design_al_thumama_stadium |title=Qatar 2022: Heerim to design Al Thumama Stadium |date=2017-04-26 |work=StadiumDB.com |accessdate=2020-11-28 |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209034625/http://stadiumdb.com/news/2017/04/qatar_2022_heerim_to_design_al_thumama_stadium |dead-url=no }}</ref>体育场的设计构思来自阿拉伯男子穿戴的传统编织帽<ref name="design">{{Cite web |url=https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/stadiums/al-thumama-stadium/design |title=Al Thumama Stadium Design |publisher=Supreme Committee for Delivery & Legacy |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207065427/https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/stadiums/al-thumama-stadium/design |dead-url=no }}</ref>，平面呈圆形，外立面由带孔的白色板组成，模仿菱形的编织图案。体育场的顶棚为张力悬索结构，覆有白色带有纹理的膜。世界杯期间，体育场可容纳4万名观众。<ref name="ornamental_facade" />体育场的比赛场地和观众席都装有空调。<ref name="heerim" />

世界杯之后，苏马迈体育场的上层看台将被拆除，将观众容量减少至2万人。<ref name="heerim">{{Cite web |url=http://www.heerim.com/project/view?id=1121&lang=en |title=Qatar Al Thumama Stadium |work=Heerim Architects & Planners |accessdate=2020-11-28 |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209003322/http://www.heerim.com/project/view?id=1121&lang=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>拆下的座椅将被捐赠给缺乏体育设施的国家。<ref name="Legacy">{{Cite web |url=https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/stadiums/al-thumama-stadium/legacy |title=Al Thumama Stadium Legacy |publisher=Supreme Committee for Delivery & Legacy |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209010812/https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/stadiums/al-thumama-stadium/legacy |dead-url=no }}</ref>体育场上层看台的位置将改建为酒店和运动医学门诊部。<ref name="heerim" />体育场外围将建设篮球、排球、手球、游泳、跑步和自行车场地，还将建设商业设施和一座清真寺。<ref name="Legacy" />

